      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2657 - Hisham ibn Salim narrated from Abu Abdullah (as), who said:\n\"If a Muhrim develops an abscess or a boil, he may lance it and treat it with oil or fat.\""
